title: Pin Ups - Lee Marvin (1997)
description:
This is a nice brazilian super-underground band from 1990's. Their music its a mix with noise, shoegazing, punk rock and grunge. Very nice and melodic. In that days Pin Ups was the hottest band from brazilian underground scene.
 This particular albun "Lee Marvin" was record without the original lead singer. All music are in english.
